      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant must be a permanent resident of Uttarakhand.\n1. The applicant must belong to the Scheduled Caste category.\n1. The applicant’s age must be between 18 and 50 years.\n1. The applicant’s annual income must not exceed ₹1,05,600/- for rural areas and ₹1,29,840/- for urban areas. \n\n",
